HackerNewsDroid
===============

This is an android application with accompanying server backend for reading Hacker News in a nice way on your android phone.

To get it up and running:

* Install django on your server, and the android dev environment somewhere.
* Get this repository.
* Make a Config.java in the android folder by changing Config.java.template.
* Start the django from the hndjango folder, and run the application on your phone.
